description:
Set of 3 Soft Copper Bookplates for scrapbooking, cardmaking, altered art, collages and more!

	3 different sizes of bookplates. These are made from a soft copper (.005 thickness) which bends easily to accomodate many handcrafted projects.

	Sizes are approximately (see photo for presentation of dimensions &#8211; measurements are taken from outside lines of rectangular plates):

	Large Bookplate: 2 5/8&#8221; <span class="caps">X 1 1</span>/4&#8221; 
Medium Bookplate: 2&#8221; <span class="caps">X 1</span>&#8221; 
Small Bookplate: 1 1/2&#8221; <span class="caps">X 1</span>&#8221;

	Nice for journaling spots, names, phrases, etc.

	Holes on each side of the bookplates allow for easy securing to your projects with brads.

	The copper will blend well with many vintage, antique and other scrapbooking or project themes.
